                                   24913  1                      Ÿ  internal format:  ("." represents a blank)                   Ÿ

                                   24921  1                      Ÿ    gguuu - account                                            Ÿ

                                   24928  1                      Ÿ    yyyyyyyyy - current ytd charges                            Ÿ

                                   24930  1                      Ÿ    ppppppppp - previous days charges                          Ÿ

0                                  54618              *
                                   54619              * chkkw verifies that the user has the right to do the access
                                   54620              * requested for another user's resource (fetch, purge,
                                   54621              * save, scratch, etc.).  the password record is read in (unless
                                   54622              * it doesn't exist) and the user is prompted for the password.
                                   54623              * if the user enters the right password, or if a privileged person
                                   54624              * enters 'ok' or 'yes', the access is permitted and a return
                                   54625              * is made with a zero return code.  otherwise the return flag
                                   54626              * is checked to see if return is to be made with a nonzero code;
                                   54627              * if no return on failure is wanted chkkw goes to cverror.
                                   54628              * if the password record does not exist, the user is denied
                                   54629              * access unless he is privileged.  if he is privileged, an 'ok?'
                                   54630              * prompt is made, to see if he really wants access.
                                   54631              *
                                   54632              * input - r1 = points to a cleared password record area with
                                   54633              *              the initials and group set.
                                   54634              *         r0 = flags (0=normal; 1=no priv bypass)
                                   54635              *
                                   54636              * output - return if access is ok, otherwise go to cverror.
                                   54637              *
                                   54638              *
 00BAC8 50E0 D000/9008_      00000 54639              CHKKW    XPROC
 USING  *,R7

                                   54685

                                   56277              Ÿ  WATCHKW -- Routine to monitor unsucessful attempts supply the      Ÿ
                                   56278              Ÿ    password.  After 20 attempts we start logging the                Ÿ
                                   56279              Ÿ    the commands, and after 40 attempts the user is logged off.      Ÿ
                                   56280              Ÿ    If there have been no attempts in the last five minutes          Ÿ
                                   56281              Ÿ    then the counter is reset.                                       Ÿ
